Scenario:
Building a high-end Computer system involves many optional components (RAM size, CPU type, SSD capacity, Graphics Card, etc.). A constructor with too many parameters (telescoping constructor) is difficult to read and maintain.

Requirements:

Product: Computer class with multiple attributes.

Builder Mechanism: An inner or dedicated builder class that allows step-by-step assembly.

Goal: Separate the construction of a complex object from its representation so that the same construction process can create different representations. This provides better control over the construction process compared to traditional constructors.